name: FrenChain
description: FrenChain is a Layer One, EVM designed by frens for frens.Many blockchains are built off of internet culture and memes, but fail to deliver a truly cozy environment. Cutthroat and competitive, cold and corporate, the frens always end up taking a backseat. That all changes today. Powered by meme magic and fueled by good vibes, gone are the days of cold, uncaring devs and admins, high fees, and slow transaction times. We prioritize all frens, our community our builders, memecoins, serious coins, nfts alike! We are building a comfy and frenly home to all that want to enjoy in the pleasure of Web3. Our philosophy and emphasis on building this environment means that our grant program will be built around those who greatly contribute to the network we are building. Expect to have access to our devs for auditing, building and growing!
